{"id":3433,"date":"2026-03-05T10:28:20","date_gmt":"2026-03-05T10:28:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/?p=3433"},"modified":"2026-03-06T13:43:35","modified_gmt":"2026-03-06T13:43:35","slug":"zakaj-so-plasticni-selitveni-zaboji-pametnejsa-izbira-od-kartona","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/zakaj-so-plasticni-selitveni-zaboji-pametnejsa-izbira-od-kartona\/","title":{"rendered":"Zakaj so plasti\u010dni selitveni zaboji pametnej\u0161a izbira od kartona?"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3433\" class=\"elementor elementor-3433\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ea0773 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8ea0773\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca798d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ca798d7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-225x300.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-2244\" alt=\"Plasti\u010dni selitveni zaboji Rabimbox za varno selitev\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-225x300.png 225w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-768x1025.png 768w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-1151x1536.png 1151w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-1535x2048.png 1535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fbb1d30 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fbb1d30\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e8a853 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4e8a853\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/izposoja\/\">Zakaj je izposoja plasti\u010dnih zabojev Rabimbox pametnej\u0161a izbira od nakupa kartona?<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f07956 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2f07956\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e4037c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e4037c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-path-to-node=\"6\">Pri vsaki selitvi se pojavi isto vpra\u0161anje: <i data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">&#8220;Kje najti dovolj mo\u010dne \u0161katle?&#8221;<\/i> Tradicionalna <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"91\">selitvena embala\u017ea<\/b> v obliki kartona nas pogosto pusti na cedilu, saj se ob ve\u010dji te\u017ei dno rado preda, ne nudi pa nobene za\u0161\u010dite pred vlago ali umazanijo. Pri Rabimboxu re\u0161ujemo ta problem z <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"281\">izposojo profesionalnih zabojev<\/b>, ki so va\u0161a najbolj\u0161a nalo\u017eba v varno selitev dragocenosti brez nepotrebnega stresa.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Glavne prednosti izposoje Rabimbox zabojev:<\/b><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"8\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Vrhunska za\u0161\u010dita va\u0161ih stvari:<\/b> Trpe\u017ena plastika varuje va\u0161e predmete pred vlago, prahom in udarci, ki so pri kartonu usodni.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Hitrost in enostavnost brez lepilnega traku:<\/b> Pozabite na ure lepljenja in sestavljanja \u0161katel \u2013 na\u0161i zaboji so pripravljeni takoj, vi jih samo nalo\u017eite in zaprete.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Maksimalna higiena in \u010disto\u010da:<\/b> Vsak zaboj po uporabi temeljito o\u010distimo in razku\u017eimo, kar zagotavlja higieno za vsako novo stranko.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Brez kopi\u010denja odpadkov:<\/b> Po selitvi zabojev ne rabite odlagati na smeti\u0161\u010de; mi jih odpeljemo, vi pa u\u017eivate v \u010distem novem domu.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong>Kako varno spakirati krhke predmete? (Re\u0161itev za miren prevoz)<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">Najve\u010dji stres pri selitvi povzro\u010da strah, da bi se dragocena vsebina, kot so kozarci, elektronika ali umetnine, med potjo po\u0161kodovala. Na\u0161a <b data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"141\">selitvena embala\u017ea<\/b> s svojo trdo lupino ta problem popolnoma odpravi, saj se ne zvija pod te\u017eo drugih zabojev.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tukaj je recept za varno pakiranje:<\/b><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"12\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Plastno zlaganje:<\/b> Na dno zaboja polo\u017eite mehkej\u0161o plast, nato te\u017eje predmete, na vrh pa najla\u017eje in najbolj krhke kose.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Brez praznega prostora:<\/b> Praznine zapolnite s papirjem ali tekstilom, da prepre\u010dite premikanje vsebine med vo\u017enjo.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Varno zlaganje v vi\u0161ino:<\/b> Za razliko od kartona lahko na\u0161e zaboje zlo\u017eite visoko enega na drugega, saj so narejeni za stabilno nalaganje brez nevarnosti sesedanja.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jasno ozna\u010devanje:<\/b> Vsak zaboj ima prostor za nalepko, kamor vpi\u0161ete vsebino (npr. &#8220;Kuhinja \u2013 krhko&#8221;), kar vam bo prihranilo ure \u010dasa pri razpakiranju.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-path-to-node=\"13\">Z izposojo pravih zabojev in uporabo tehnik profesionalcev bo va\u0161a selitev hitra, varna in ekolo\u0161ko odgovorna.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71ab425 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"71ab425\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-821ef00 elementor-button-info elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"821ef00\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Naro\u010di selitvene zaboje<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e2066f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8e2066f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a96df6f elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"a96df6f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Zakaj je izposoja plasti\u010dnih zabojev Rabimbox pametnej\u0161a izbira od nakupa kartona? Pri vsaki selitvi se pojavi isto vpra\u0161anje: &#8220;Kje najti dovolj mo\u010dne \u0161katle?&#8221; Tradicionalna selitvena embala\u017ea v obliki kartona nas pogosto pusti na cedilu, saj se ob ve\u010dji te\u017ei dno rado preda, ne nudi pa nobene za\u0161\u010dite pred vlago ali umazanijo. Pri Rabimboxu re\u0161ujemo ta [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"elementor_header_footer","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"disabled","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"disabled","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":